[l] Scifi des Tages: Wenn die Feuerwehr nicht mit Wasserschlaeuchen sondern mit einer Stereoanlage und Lautsprechern anrueckt.  Das ist ja mal abgefahren!The basic concept, Tran said, is that sound waves are also “pressure waves, and they displace some of the oxygen” as they travel through the air. Oxygen, we all recall from high school chemistry, fuels fire. At a certain frequency, the sound waves “separate the oxygen [in the fire] from the fuel. The pressure wave is going back and forth, and that agitates where the air is. That specific space is enough to keep the fire from reigniting.”
